  },
  {
    question: 'Does cloud breeder software support species other than dogs?',
    answer: 'Some platforms focus exclusively on dogs. Others support multiple species including cats, horses, goats, rabbits, sheep, alpacas, and llamas. Check species support before committing.'
  },
  {
    question: 'Can multiple co-breeders share one cloud breeding account?',
    answer: 'Many platforms allow multiple users with different permission levels. If you manage a program with partners, look for team access or co-breeder features.'
  },
  {
