    answer: 'Reputable cloud platforms use encryption and secure hosting. Review the provider\'s security practices and data handling policies before signing up.'
  },
  {
    question: 'Can cloud breeder software connect to OFA, AKC, or breed registries?',
    answer: 'Some platforms offer passthrough links to public registry records so buyers can verify health testing or registration at the source. Not all platforms have this capability.'
  }
];
